{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0028","text":"從未了解你 我偏再縱寵你","structure":{"line_index":28,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["縱容","不被理解","關係問題"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["縱寵","瞭解"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,9,5,5,3,4,4,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","mei6","liu5","gaai2","nei5","ngo5","pin1","zoi3","zung3","cung2","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"瞭解","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"縱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"寵","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「我」反思自己過去對「你」的縱容，以及「你」的不理解。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0027","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0029","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0029","text":"我也太縱你 你當我已死","structure":{"line_index":29,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["縱容","被忽視","關係破裂"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["縱你","當我已死"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,4,5,5,5,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","jaa5","taai3","zung3","nei5","nei5","ngo5","ji5","sei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"太","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"縱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"當","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"已","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"死","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「我」認為自己過度縱容「你」，而「你」卻將「我」視若無睹。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0028","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0030","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0030","text":"別日夜在妒忌 假得你","structure":{"line_index":30,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["嫉妒","虛偽","指責"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["妒忌","假"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,2,4,2,9,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bit6","jat6","je6","zoi6","dou3","gei6","gaa2","dak1","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"別","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"日夜","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"妒忌","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"假得","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"指責「你」的嫉妒是虛假的，語氣帶有不滿。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0029","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0031","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0031","text":"我也有吻過你 是爲着好奇","structure":{"line_index":31,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["好奇","關係探索"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["吻","好奇"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,5,4,5,2,2,9,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","jaa5","jau5","man5","gwo3","nei5","si6","zoek6","hou2","kei4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"PART"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"爲","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"好奇","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「我」解釋過去的親密行為是出於好奇，而非真情。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0030","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0032","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0032","text":"天都知 你與我 誰人有理","structure":{"line_index":32,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["對質","釐清關係"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["誰人","有理"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,5,5,5,0,0,5,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","dou1","zi1","nei5","jyu5","ngo5","seoi4","jan4","jau5","lei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天都知","pos":"INTJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"與","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"有理","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"強調事實清楚，質疑誰對誰錯，暗示「你」無理取鬧。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0031","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0033","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0033","text":"天天想你 才叫你妒忌","structure":{"line_index":33,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["嫉妒","佔有慾"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["天天想","妒忌"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,9,5,0,4,5,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","tin1","soeng2","nei5","coi4","giu3","nei5","dou3","gei6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"才","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"妒忌","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「我」認為「你」天天想著「我」，才導致「你」的嫉妒。"},"source":{"title":"滾","artists":["楊千嬅"],"lyricists":["梁漢文","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2260","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0032","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2o5Y2D5ayF_MjI2MA_0034","paragraph_id":"para_09"}}
